about.summary: A utility for serialization of python objects.

name: dill
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "0.2.5" %}

package:
    name: dill
    version: {{ version }}

source:
    fn: dill-{{ version }}.tgz
    url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/d/dill/dill-{{ version }}.tgz
    md5: 5b0c312f034914be2e230457747d9b6c

build:
    number: 1
    script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt

requirements:
    build:
        - python
        - setuptools
    run:
        - pyreadline  # [win]
        - python

test:
    imports:
        - dill

about:
    home: http://www.cacr.caltech.edu/~mmckerns
    license: BSD 3-Clause
    summary: 'A utility for serialization of python objects.'

extra:
    recipe-maintainers:
        - DanCodigaMWRA
        - ocefpaf
